{"tid":1277670,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"有朋友發夢尋晚去左金鐘，返到屋企聽一首歌聽到喊哂","createTime":"2019-07-02T08:50:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-02T09:23:34.000Z","uid":264908,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"1080c54cbcd770a344ca4087eb23577289e50b37","tid":1277670,"uid":264908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T08:50:16.000Z","msg":"轉載自朋友對話，對方屋企長期開住大台，對於n年前既亞視星光大道係一d共鳴都無。尋晚返到屋企覺得好靜好唔慣，戴住耳機長開住youtube聽歌，屋企人係藍底，次次講親政治野都會鬧交，所以尋晚都唔敢講自己去邊，淨係話約左朋友食飯。<br />\n<br />\n「明亮如星光 能燃亮你麼」、「白日夢做過幾多 哪怕你笑我現況」、「用雙手拆掉攔阻 我要怕甚麼」好多句都好中，個腦即刻諗起好多畫面<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/emNESi9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FemNESi9.jpg&h=52337c1d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n[<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Hb-EK-rK3-Q]\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FHb-EK-rK3-Q%5D&d=Mrz8gheyF4cbCiJyPb%2FME6pJ2kzo9njAZIZZFH2Kh%2FI%3D&h=eac97f66\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/Hb-EK-rK3-Q]</a>"},{"pid":"6293cab1d408b77e4d2f034480582afb3e1c37fc","tid":1277670,"uid":73730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T08:57:36.000Z","msg":"唔識宜首歌<br />\n我係老餅，琴日全日諗住<br />\n<br />\nDo you hear the people sing"},{"pid":"fa7cfe5f994ac614abcdb7f5a2b998b057932190","tid":1277670,"uid":264908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6293cab1d408b77e4d2f034480582afb3e1c37fc","tid":1277670,"uid":73730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T08:57:36.000Z","msg":"唔識宜首歌<br />\n我係老餅，琴日全日諗住<br />\n<br />\nDo you hear the people sing"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T09:23:34.000Z","msg":"可能係歌詞有共鳴"}]}